snippet.title: C-Smash VRS Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Summer Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
C-Smash VRS lets you play squash in space and is coming to PS VR 2 on June 23, 2023. A new trailer for the game debuted during the Summer Showcase. You can also check out a free demo for the game on the PlayStation Store.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS
